     F** EDSR15 ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY - SAVE AB#WP15 TO AB#PP15        *
     F*  WRITTEN: LEC                                      *
     F*           09/02/2021                               *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     FAB#WP15 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAB#PP15 O   E                    DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140D#TIME
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      * INITIAL SETTING
     C                     TIME           D#TIME
      * SAVE AB#WP15 --------------------------------------
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN99
     C           *IN99     DOWEQ*OFF
     C                     READ AB#WP15                  99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     EWCRDT
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       EWCRTM
     C                     WRITEAB#PP151
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
